title: Coding Math: Episode 58 - Array Math
author: Coding Math
description:
Coding Math is an ongoing series of video tutorials designed to teach you the math you need to understand as a programmer.

Most programmers understand the language they are coding in, but often stumble on the mathematics they need to use to achieve various visual effects, motion, etc. Coding Math helps explain these in a clear, easy to understand way, with real world code you can use in your own projects.

JavaScript is the language of choice at this time, but the principles can be applied to nearly any programming language.
